{"tid":1482401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［澳洲即日來港遊行］見證完墨爾本支那踩場之後，而家即日來回返香港參加818","createTime":"2019-08-18T05:29:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T05:39:29.000Z","uid":152084,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e676891d7f4298690f28589a469a3dd2d275f2d1","tid":1482401,"uid":152084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:29:39.000Z","msg":"屋企人係澳洲讀書，今日突然返左黎，嚇x死我，原來係琴日決定同frd係墨爾本返香港快閃818遊行，今晚就飛返墨爾本。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">見證著外國支那如何踩場，今日自己主場點都唔可以輸</span>。今晚就飛走，佢話會早d去機場check in先，唔介意大家今晚去送佢機，今晚12點幾先飛。<br />\n<br />\n係外國既手足都即日飛返黎，住係香港既你唔係連搭地鐵去遊行都唔願意掛！ <br />\n<br />\n等陣維園見！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CH1QySO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCH1QySO.png&h=75f75705&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2fe840d0b8340920bc32fc03ca79958c59bd38d","tid":1482401,"uid":6840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:30:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e546950febfbcd43ec3e3942c0c989e695ad6e86","tid":1482401,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:30:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49483e744fb109d7169c9350f24c0532184a48fa","tid":1482401,"uid":117856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:31:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b69b1cf9c7ae73fb1b3bdcfbd04862a3863b6dba","tid":1482401,"uid":20338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:32:13.000Z","msg":"佩服 加油啦"},{"pid":"d109d715ea4c58f7154ce7071d984439eb181d2c","tid":1482401,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a558bc66ea5d0770